'''α-氨基己二酸'''（{{lang-en|α-Aminoadipic acid}}）是代谢[[赖氨酸|赖氨酸]]和[[酵母氨酸|酵母氨酸]]的{{le|α-氨基己二酸途径|α-Aminoadipic acid pathway}}的中间产物，由{{le|氨基己二酸氨基转移酶|aminoadipate aminotransferase}}催化[[高异柠檬酸|高异柠檬酸]]生成，再由{{le|L-氨基己二酸半醛脱氢酶|L-aminoadipate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase|氨基乙二酸还原酶}}还原为[[阿離胺酸|阿離胺酸]]。

2013年的一项研究确定了α-氨基己二酸是糖尿病发展的一种新型预测因子<!-- 原文 novel predictor -->，可作为人类体内葡萄糖体内稳态的调节剂。<ref name="Wang">{{cite journal |title=2-Aminoadipic acid is a biomarker for diabetes risk |author=Wang TJ, Ngo D, Psychogios N, Dejam A, Larson MG, Vasan RS, Ghorbani A, O'Sullivan J, Cheng S, Rhee EP, Sinha S, McCabe E, Fox CS, O'Donnell CJ, Ho JE, Florez JC, Magnusson M, Pierce KA, Souza AL, Yu Y, Carter C, Light PE, Melander O, Clish CB, Gerszten RE |journal=J Clin Invest |volume=123 |issue=10 |pages=4309–4317 |year=2013 |pmid=24091325 |url=http://www.jci.org/articles/view/64801 |doi=10.1172/JCI64801 |pmc=3784523 |access-date=2014-10-15 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214130642/https://www.jci.org/articles/view/64801 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

